query: SELECT DATE_FORMAT(createdAt, '%Y-%m') as ym, MONTH(createdAt) as m, count(*) as cnt FROM inquiries WHERE createdAt >= '2025-09-01 00:00:00' GROUP BY DATE_FORMAT(createdAt, '%Y-%m'), MONTH(createdAt) ORDER BY DATE_FORMAT(createdAt, '%Y-%m')
